<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/detail.css">
    <title>My shows list</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="mb-5">
        <%- include('./templates/navigation.ejs') %> 
    </header>


    <main class="bg p-4">

        <div class="shows-header mb-4 d-flex justify-content-between">
            <h2>Star Wars</h2>
            <h2>Rating: 7.3</h2>
        </div>


        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-12 col-sm-5 img-column">
                <img src="https://images4.alphacoders.com/653/thumb-1920-653613.jpg" alt="">
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                <p>When carefree Nyles and reluctant maid of honor Sarah have a chance encounter at a Palm Springs wedding, things get complicated when they find themselves unable to escape the venue, themselves, or each other.",</p>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-1">
                    <span><span class="first-word">Release</span> date: 20-20-2020</span>
                    <span><span class="first-word">NSFW</span>: False</span>
                    <span class="mb-3"><span class="first-word">Popularity</span>: 15,000</span>
                    <form action="">
                        <input type="hidden" name="showId" value="x">
                        <input type="hidden" name="showType">
                        <input class="text-light fw-bold" type="submit" value="Add to list">
                    </form>
                </div>


            </div>

        </div>


    </main>


</body>
</html>